OL,3,C'I feel brilliant!': Burma veteran
OL,4,Ccelebrates 103rd birthday
OL,6,FA Burma veteran says he "feels
OL,7,Fbrilliant" after turning 103 years old.
OL,9,FJames Fenton served as a bombardier in
OL,10,Fthe 178 Field Regiment of the Royal
OL,11,FArtillery, and was deployed in Burma
OL,12,Faged 20.
OL,14,FThe centenarian is one of the last
OL,15,Fremaining Burma veterans in the world,
OL,16,Fa group of soldiers often referred to
OL,17,Fas the 'forgotten army'.
OL,19,FSince leaving the army, Mr Fenton has
OL,20,Flived in the Isle of Man - at first in
OL,21,FPort Erin and now in Douglas.
