OL,3,C'I feel brilliant!': Burma veteran
OL,4,Ccelebrates 103rd birthday
OL,6,FWhile fighting in the Second World
OL,7,FWar, he would often document his time
OL,8,Fas a soldier with artwork and
OL,9,Fphotographs.
OL,11,FDuring his service, he would regularly
OL,12,Fwrite letters to his parents, take
OL,13,Fphotographs and paint pictures of his
OL,14,Fsurroundings.
OL,16,FHe then later sorted through his
OL,17,Fparents house following their death in
OL,18,F1980, and discovered the letters he
OL,19,Fhad sent to them during the Second
OL,20,FWorld War.
