OL,3,C'I feel brilliant!': Burma veteran
OL,4,Ccelebrates 103rd birthday
OL,6,FHis work has since been compiled into
OL,7,Fa book called 'The Forgotten Army'
OL,8,Ffeaturing many of his creations, and
OL,9,Fcopies of the letters he sent.
OL,11,FIn 2022, Mr Fenton travelled to the
OL,12,FCenotaph in London for Remembrance Day
OL,13,Fat 100 year's old.
OL,15,FDespite his age, he marched alongside
OL,16,Fthe few remaining veterans to pay his
OL,17,Frespects.
